## Which License Do I Need?

| You are... | License Needed |
|------------|----------------|
| University researcher | Academic (Free) |
| Graduate student | Academic (Free) |
| Non-profit research institute | Academic (Free) |
| Government research lab | Academic (Free) |
| Pharma/biotech company | Commercial (Paid) |
| Contract research organization | Commercial (Paid) |
| Diagnostics company | Commercial (Paid) |
| Startup using for product development | Commercial (Paid) |
| Consultant billing clients | Commercial (Paid) |

